      "content_license": "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body": "<p>This simple approach you can use to put the cursor end of the edit text</p>\n<p><strong>Kotlin code</strong></p>\n<p>// Getting the Edit Text View</p>\n<pre><code>val editText = findViewById&lt;EditText&gt;(R.id.my_edit_text)\n</code></pre>\n<p>// Get the current text</p>\n<pre><code>val text = editText.text.toString()\n</code></pre>\n<p>// Set the text with a space character at the end</p>\n<pre><code>editText.setText(&quot;$text &quot;)\n</code></pre>\n<p>// Move the cursor to the end of the text</p>\n<pre><code>editText.setSelection(text.length + 1)\n</code></pre>\n<hr />\n<p><em><strong>Java Code</strong></em></p>\n<p>// Get the EditText view</p>\n<pre><code>EditText editText = findViewById(R.id.my_edit_text);;\n</code></pre>\n<p>// Get the current text</p>\n<pre><code>String text = editText.getText().toString();\n</code></pre>\n<p>// Set the text with a space character at the end</p>\n<pre><code>editText.setText(text + &quot; &quot;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>// Move the cursor to the end of the text</p>\n<pre><code>editText.setSelection(text.length() + 1);\n</code></pre>\n"
    }
